ARBOVIRUS POSITIONS AVAILABLE - USA (NEW YORK STATE)
***********************************
A ProMED-mail post

Date: Tue 1 Feb 2000
From: Jack Woodall <woodall@promedmail.org>

The New York State Health Department is advertising URGENTLY for staff to expand
its capacity for arbovirus surveillance & diagnosis, in preparation for the
possible return of West Nile encephalitis in the spring.
The deadline for most applications is *** 11 Feb 2000 ***
The positions available are:
Assistant Research Scientist (3 Positions)
Entomological Assistant (2 Positions)- hourly paid
Laboratory Technician
Research Scientist 1 (2 Positions)
Research Scientist 2 (2 positions)
Research Scientist 3
Research Scientist 4 (lab chief grade)
For further information go to:
<http://www.health.state.ny.us/nysdoh/phforum/jobs/employ.htm>
--
Jack Woodall
<woodall@promedmail.org>
(retiring from position as Director, NYS Arbovirus Laboratory, on 26 Feb 2000)
.......................jw
http://www.compuland.com.br
